<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtsensors-tiltsensor.xml">TiltSensor</db:link> element reports tilt events along the X and Y axes.</db:para>
<db:para>This element wraps the <db:link xlink:href="qtiltsensor.xml">QTiltSensor</db:link> class. Please see the documentation for <db:link xlink:href="qtiltsensor.xml">QTiltSensor</db:link> for details.</db:para>
